 {"id":"bd-l1sr3","title":"add mounted-path read-only EROFS coverage for ext4 mutation ioctls","description":"Survey finding: `ffs-fuse` already has direct dispatch tests showing that read-only mounts reject mutation ioctls like `EXT4_IOC_SETFLAGS` and `EXT4_IOC_MOVE_EXT` with `EROFS` before backend dispatch. The mounted-path harness currently covers the writable success/rejection contracts, but it does not prove the operator-visible read-only fast-fail path.

